{
  "stem": "14251.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I have to quit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I can't tell that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "You have to cut it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I didn't know if they were going to murder her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, my mind wasn't adult enough to know anything about, say, rape or any of this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These are all things that children feel an underlying threat about, but they don't really know it in a conscious sense.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all I know is my mother was gone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And immediately, Mama Subitski began to pray all kinds of prayers and-- that I wasn't familiar with about praying at this point anymore.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's-- that was long in-- in the past.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said, she will be back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She will be back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The following evening she came back in the door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, we just couldn't believe that since none of the others had come back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "These details really were never revealed by her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I assure you that thereafter, when the Russians separated us from the Subitskis, we learned-- yeah, in the last decade I found out that it was a direct Stalin order.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If they speak German, treat them like Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "See, we did not know these things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they didn't believe who we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The only people who believed us were periodically meeting Russian Jewish officers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Fortunately, there was a good number of these.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It nevertheless happened that we were separated from them, just in the simple sorting of people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Everybody's afraid enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They're not going to ask why.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my mother's attempts were futile.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She never succeeded in getting any help for them or to keep us together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We wanted to stay with-- together with them so that nothing would happen to them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We didn't know if they were going to shoot civilians or what.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
